# Diamond scheduled jobs — install on the host with:  crontab deploy/crontab.example
# (or paste into `crontab -e`). CRON_TZ requires Vixie/cronie (Debian/Ubuntu default).
#
# ONE-TIME bulk backfill on a fresh box (NOT scheduled below): these only ever ingest the
# current day incrementally, so a new deploy starts with no history. Without it the workload
# model stays inactive (no pitcher_starts → null pitcher_projections.workload), and the prop
# board renders every pitcher pick as a bogus 100% under. Run once after first deploy:
#   ./deploy/run-ingester.sh backfill-games --start 2023-03-01 --end <today>
#   ./deploy/run-ingester.sh backfill-pitcher-starts --start 2023-03-01
CRON_TZ=America/New_York
DIAMOND_DIR=/opt/diamond
# Optional offsite backup target (rclone remote:bucket). When set, backup.sh mirrors each
# nightly dump there. Configure the rclone remote on the host first (e.g. `rclone config`).
# DIAMOND_B2_REMOTE=diamond-b2:diamond-backups

# Morning full run: build today's slate + close out the prior day
# (final scores, stats, picks scoring, accuracy snapshot).
0 9 * * *        /opt/diamond/deploy/run-ingester.sh daily

# Afternoon/evening quick loop (noon–11pm ET): confirmed lineups + odds + re-projection
# as lineups post. Runs through late starts: each game is only projected once its lineup
# is up (~2-3 h before first pitch), so a 10pm ET game (lineup ~8pm ET) needs ticks past
# 6pm. The projector defers a game until ~2 h before its first pitch and skips it if it's
# postponed/suspended/cancelled. Each tick also grades TODAY's recorded picks against
# final scores/stats as games finish, so the home board's ✓/✗ markers update live.
*/30 12-23 * * *  /opt/diamond/deploy/run-ingester.sh daily --quick

# Weekly projection-prior refresh (Mon 8am ET, before the 9am daily run): pull the
# external systems (Steamer/THE BAT X/ATC/ZiPS) from FanGraphs, bank a dated snapshot
# for later leak-free backtesting, then re-blend. blend-priors only runs if the fetch
# succeeds. The live model still uses the Marcel prior until the blend is validated.
0 8 * * 1        /opt/diamond/deploy/run-ingester.sh refresh-projections && /opt/diamond/deploy/run-ingester.sh blend-priors

# Model feature aggregates (pitch-matchup arsenals, batted-ball/barrel, bat-tracking).
# These are NOT part of `daily`, so schedule them at 8:30am ET — just before the 9am
# daily run — so today's projections use fresh inputs. They aggregate from the Statcast
# cache (no big re-download), so each is quick.
30 8 * * *       /opt/diamond/deploy/run-ingester.sh refresh-pitch-aggregations && /opt/diamond/deploy/run-ingester.sh refresh-batted-ball && /opt/diamond/deploy/run-ingester.sh refresh-bat-tracking

# Nightly database backup.
30 3 * * *       /opt/diamond/deploy/backup.sh
